  <RI_Building_InfiniteCrystal.label>古修聚元鼎</RI_Building_InfiniteCrystal.label>
  <!-- EN: From the ancient cultivator of the creation, the researchers found Qi residue, and then reverse-study this ancient cultivator once cast giant Ding.\n\nThis Ding can absorb thin Qi from the atmosphere and condense it into a spirit crystal, which can be described as the creation of extraordinary workmanship. -->
  <RI_Building_InfiniteCrystal.description>从古修造物中，研究人员发现了灵气残留，之后逆向研究出了这种古修曾经铸造过的巨鼎。\n\n聚元鼎可以从大气中吸收稀薄的灵气，将其凝聚成灵石，可谓是鬼斧神工的造物。</RI_Building_InfiniteCrystal.description>
  
